{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":706,"text":"Some of my most wonderful memories of childhood"},{"time":3417,"text":"are of spending time with my grandmother, Mamar,"},{"time":6968,"text":"in our four-family home in Brooklyn, New York."},{"time":10768,"text":"Her apartment was an oasis."},{"time":13843,"text":"It was a place where I could sneak a cup of coffee,"},{"time":15888,"text":"which was really warm milk \nwith just a touch of caffeine."},{"time":19769,"text":"She loved life."},{"time":22303,"text":"And although she worked in a factory,"},{"time":24798,"text":"she saved her pennies and she traveled to Europe."},{"time":27970,"text":"And I remember poring over those pictures with her"},{"time":31299,"text":"and then dancing with her to her favorite music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35411,"text":"And then, when I was eight and she was 60,"},{"time":40033,"text":"something changed."},{"time":42086,"text":"She no longer worked or traveled."},{"time":44440,"text":"She no longer danced."},{"time":46131,"text":"There were no more coffee times."},{"time":48884,"text":"My mother missed work and took her to doctors"},{"time":51068,"text":"who couldn't make a diagnosis."},{"time":53454,"text":"And my father, who worked at night, \nwould spend every afternoon with her,"},{"time":58791,"text":"just to make sure she ate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61876,"text":"Her care became all-consuming for our family."},{"time":66576,"text":"And by the time a diagnosis was made,"},{"time":68223,"text":"she was in a deep spiral."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70928,"text":"Now many of you will recognize her symptoms."},{"time":74489,"text":"My grandmother had depression."},{"time":77152,"text":"A deep, life-altering depression,"},{"time":80472,"text":"from which she never recovered."},{"time":83562,"text":"And back then, so little \nwas known about depression."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87253,"text":"But even today, 50 years later,"},{"time":90658,"text":"there's still so much more to learn."},{"time":93932,"text":"Today, we know that women \nare 70 percent more likely"},{"time":98840,"text":"to experience depression over their lifetimes"},{"time":101831,"text":"compared with men."},{"time":104112,"text":"And even with this high prevalence,"},{"time":106952,"text":"women are misdiagnosed between \n30 and 50 percent of the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113239,"text":"Now we know that women are more likely"},{"time":116172,"text":"to experience the symptoms \nof fatigue, sleep disturbance,"},{"time":121560,"text":"pain and anxiety compared with men."},{"time":124105,"text":"And these symptoms are often overlooked"},{"time":126804,"text":"as symptoms of depression."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129767,"text":"And it isn't only depression in which \nthese sex differences occur,"},{"time":133550,"text":"but they occur across so many diseases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138069,"text":"So it's my grandmother's struggles"},{"time":140064,"text":"that have really led me on a lifelong quest."},{"time":143797,"text":"And today, I lead a center in which the mission"},{"time":147025,"text":"is to discover why these sex differences occur"},{"time":150804,"text":"and to use that knowledge"},{"time":152906,"text":"to improve the health of women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155865,"text":"Today, we know that every cell has a sex."},{"time":159998,"text":"Now, that's a term coined \nby the Institute of Medicine."},{"time":163951,"text":"And what it means is that \nmen and women are different"},{"time":167712,"text":"down to the cellular and molecular levels."},{"time":172154,"text":"It means that we're different \nacross all of our organs."},{"time":177094,"text":"From our brains to our hearts, our lungs, our joints."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182589,"text":"Now, it was only 20 years ago"},{"time":186473,"text":"that we hardly had any data on women's health"},{"time":190300,"text":"beyond our reproductive functions."},{"time":193183,"text":"But then in 1993,"},{"time":196084,"text":"the NIH Revitalization Act was signed into law."},{"time":200696,"text":"And what this law did was it mandated"},{"time":203299,"text":"that women and minorities \nbe included in clinical trials"},{"time":207772,"text":"that were funded by the National Institutes of Health."},{"time":211823,"text":"And in many ways, the law has worked."},{"time":214750,"text":"Women are now routinely \nincluded in clinical studies,"},{"time":218420,"text":"and we've learned that there are major differences"},{"time":220671,"text":"in the ways that women and men"},{"time":222764,"text":"experience disease."},{"time":225300,"text":"But remarkably,"},{"time":227465,"text":"what we have learned about these \ndifferences is often overlooked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232559,"text":"So, we have to ask ourselves the question:"},{"time":236384,"text":"Why leave women's health to chance?"},{"time":240897,"text":"And we're leaving it to chance in two ways."},{"time":243540,"text":"The first is that there is so much more to learn"},{"time":247237,"text":"and we're not making the investment"},{"time":249646,"text":"in fully understanding the extent \nof these sex differences."},{"time":253814,"text":"And the second is that we aren't \ntaking what we have learned,"},{"time":258536,"text":"and routinely applying it in clinical care."},{"time":262240,"text":"We are just not doing enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266229,"text":"So, I'm going to share with you three examples"},{"time":268488,"text":"of where sex differences have \nimpacted the health of women,"},{"time":272194,"text":"and where we need to do more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274864,"text":"Let's start with heart disease."},{"time":276876,"text":"It's the number one killer of women \nin the United States today."},{"time":282078,"text":"This is the face of heart disease."},{"time":284974,"text":"Linda is a middle-aged woman,"},{"time":287255,"text":"who had a stent placed in one of the arteries"},{"time":289840,"text":"going to her heart."},{"time":291940,"text":"When she had recurring symptoms \nshe went back to her doctor."},{"time":295191,"text":"Her doctor did the gold standard test:"},{"time":297829,"text":"a cardiac catheterization."},{"time":300116,"text":"It showed no blockages."},{"time":302533,"text":"Linda's symptoms continued."},{"time":304605,"text":"She had to stop working."},{"time":307078,"text":"And that's when she found us."},{"time":309830,"text":"When Linda came to us, we did \nanother cardiac catheterization"},{"time":313978,"text":"and this time, we found clues."},{"time":317395,"text":"But we needed another test"},{"time":319869,"text":"to make the diagnosis."},{"time":322463,"text":"So we did a test called an intracoronary ultrasound,"},{"time":327043,"text":"where you use soundwaves to look at the artery"},{"time":329348,"text":"from the inside out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332079,"text":"And what we found"},{"time":334017,"text":"was that Linda's disease didn't look like"},{"time":336468,"text":"the typical male disease."},{"time":339538,"text":"The typical male disease looks like this."},{"time":342734,"text":"There's a discrete blockage or stenosis."},{"time":346046,"text":"Linda's disease, like the disease of so many women,"},{"time":350347,"text":"looks like this."},{"time":352189,"text":"The plaque is laid down more evenly, more diffusely"},{"time":355726,"text":"along the artery, and it's harder to see."},{"time":359698,"text":"So for Linda, and for so many women,"},{"time":363104,"text":"the gold standard test wasn't gold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366796,"text":"Now, Linda received the right treatment."},{"time":369783,"text":"She went back to her life and, fortunately, today"},{"time":371961,"text":"she is doing well."},{"time":373713,"text":"But Linda was lucky."},{"time":375319,"text":"She found us, we found her disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377945,"text":"But for too many women, that's not the case."},{"time":380856,"text":"We have the tools."},{"time":383171,"text":"We have the technology to make the diagnosis."},{"time":386852,"text":"But it's all too often that these sex diffferences"},{"time":390249,"text":"are overlooked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392553,"text":"So what about treatment?"},{"time":394726,"text":"A landmark study that was published two years ago"},{"time":397436,"text":"asked the very important question:"},{"time":399858,"text":"What are the most effective treatments \nfor heart disease in women?"},{"time":404913,"text":"The authors looked at papers \nwritten over a 10-year period,"},{"time":408572,"text":"and hundreds had to be thrown out."},{"time":411050,"text":"And what they found out was that \nof those that were tossed out,"},{"time":415823,"text":"65 percent were excluded"},{"time":419477,"text":"because even though women \nwere included in the studies,"},{"time":423841,"text":"the analysis didn't differentiate \nbetween women and men."},{"time":430197,"text":"What a lost opportunity."},{"time":433418,"text":"The money had been spent"},{"time":435449,"text":"and we didn't learn how women fared."},{"time":437596,"text":"And these studies could not contribute one iota"},{"time":440397,"text":"to the very, very important question,"},{"time":442814,"text":"what are the most effective treatments"},{"time":445205,"text":"for heart disease in women?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":448100,"text":"I want to introduce you to \nHortense, my godmother,"},{"time":453592,"text":"Hung Wei, a relative of a colleague,"},{"time":457035,"text":"and somebody you may recognize --"},{"time":459226,"text":"Dana, Christopher Reeve's wife."},{"time":462873,"text":"All three women have something \nvery important in common."},{"time":467233,"text":"All three were diagnosed with lung cancer,"},{"time":470808,"text":"the number one cancer killer of women"},{"time":473737,"text":"in the United States today."},{"time":476438,"text":"All three were nonsmokers."},{"time":480314,"text":"Sadly, Dana and Hung Wei died of their disease."},{"time":485480,"text":"Today, what we know is that women who are\nnonsmokers are three times more likely"},{"time":491620,"text":"to be diagnosed with lung cancer than are men"},{"time":494357,"text":"who are nonsmokers."},{"time":496343,"text":"Now interestingly, when women are \ndiagnosed with lung cancer,"},{"time":500033,"text":"their survival tends to be better than that of men."},{"time":503212,"text":"Now, here are some clues."},{"time":505087,"text":"Our investigators have found that there are"},{"time":507486,"text":"certain genes in the lung tumor \ncells of both women and men."},{"time":512158,"text":"And these genes are activated"},{"time":514350,"text":"mainly by estrogen."},{"time":516440,"text":"And when these genes are over-expressed,"},{"time":519258,"text":"it's associated with improved survival"},{"time":521989,"text":"only in young women."},{"time":524656,"text":"Now this is a very early finding"},{"time":526330,"text":"and we don't yet know whether it has relevance"},{"time":529973,"text":"to clinical care."},{"time":532414,"text":"But it's findings like this that may provide hope"},{"time":536273,"text":"and may provide an opportunity to save lives"},{"time":539040,"text":"of both women and men."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541587,"text":"Now, let me share with you an example"},{"time":542968,"text":"of when we do consider sex differences,\nit can drive the science."},{"time":546946,"text":"Several years ago a new lung cancer drug"},{"time":549274,"text":"was being evaluated,"},{"time":550920,"text":"and when the authors looked \nat whose tumors shrank,"},{"time":555292,"text":"they found that 82 percent were women."},{"time":558725,"text":"This led them to ask the question: Well, why?"},{"time":561688,"text":"And what they found"},{"time":563243,"text":"was that the genetic mutations \nthat the drug targeted"},{"time":566723,"text":"were far more common in women."},{"time":569450,"text":"And what this has led to"},{"time":571149,"text":"is a more personalized approach"},{"time":573331,"text":"to the treatment of lung cancer \nthat also includes sex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577485,"text":"This is what we can accomplish"},{"time":579580,"text":"when we don't leave women's health to chance."},{"time":583406,"text":"We know that when you invest in research,"},{"time":586614,"text":"you get results."},{"time":588140,"text":"Take a look at the death rate \nfrom breast cancer over time."},{"time":592648,"text":"And now take a look at the death rates"},{"time":594573,"text":"from lung cancer in women over time."},{"time":597905,"text":"Now let's look at the dollars \ninvested in breast cancer --"},{"time":601515,"text":"these are the dollars invested per death --"},{"time":604484,"text":"and the dollars invested in lung cancer."},{"time":608712,"text":"Now, it's clear that our investment in breast cancer"},{"time":613633,"text":"has produced results."},{"time":615422,"text":"They may not be fast enough,"},{"time":617755,"text":"but it has produced results."},{"time":619981,"text":"We can do the same"},{"time":621785,"text":"for lung cancer and for every other disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":626776,"text":"So let's go back to depression."},{"time":630102,"text":"Depression is the number one cause"},{"time":632412,"text":"of disability in women in the world today."},{"time":637004,"text":"Our investigators have found"},{"time":639139,"text":"that there are differences in the brains"},{"time":640955,"text":"of women and men"},{"time":642432,"text":"in the areas that are connected with mood."},{"time":645551,"text":"And when you put men and women"},{"time":647624,"text":"in a functional MRI scanner --"},{"time":649499,"text":"that's the kind of scanner that shows how the brain is functioning when it's activated --"},{"time":654046,"text":"so you put them in the scanner \nand you expose them to stress."},{"time":658089,"text":"You can actually see the difference."},{"time":661976,"text":"And it's findings like this"},{"time":664505,"text":"that we believe hold some of the clues"},{"time":667486,"text":"for why we see these very significant sex differences"},{"time":671239,"text":"in depression."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673493,"text":"But even though we know"},{"time":675051,"text":"that these differences occur,"},{"time":677918,"text":"66 percent"},{"time":680571,"text":"of the brain research that begins in animals"},{"time":684567,"text":"is done in either male animals"},{"time":686893,"text":"or animals in whom the sex is not identified."}]},{"cues":[{"time":691240,"text":"So, I think we have to ask again the question:"},{"time":694859,"text":"Why leave women's health to chance?"},{"time":699661,"text":"And this is a question that haunts those of us"},{"time":702489,"text":"in science and medicine"},{"time":704300,"text":"who believe that we are on the verge \nof being able to dramatically improve"},{"time":710659,"text":"the health of women."},{"time":712335,"text":"We know that every cell has a sex."},{"time":714821,"text":"We know that these differences \nare often overlooked."},{"time":717763,"text":"And therefore we know that women \nare not getting the full benefit"},{"time":722051,"text":"of modern science and medicine today."},{"time":725950,"text":"We have the tools"},{"time":727601,"text":"but we lack the collective will and momentum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731483,"text":"Women's health is an equal rights issue"},{"time":734227,"text":"as important as equal pay."},{"time":737781,"text":"And it's an issue of the quality"},{"time":739965,"text":"and the integrity of science and medicine."},{"time":743120,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":750583,"text":"So imagine the momentum we could achieve"},{"time":755128,"text":"in advancing the health of women"},{"time":757239,"text":"if we considered whether these \nsex differences were present"},{"time":760098,"text":"at the very beginning of designing research."},{"time":763687,"text":"Or if we analyzed our data by sex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767566,"text":"So, people often ask me:"},{"time":769514,"text":"What can I do?"},{"time":771285,"text":"And here's what I suggest:"},{"time":773619,"text":"First, I suggest that you think about women's health"},{"time":777792,"text":"in the same way"},{"time":779535,"text":"that you think and care about other \ncauses that are important to you."},{"time":785580,"text":"And second, and equally as important,"},{"time":788762,"text":"that as a woman,"},{"time":790974,"text":"you have to ask your doctor"},{"time":793615,"text":"and the doctors who are caring \nfor those who you love:"},{"time":798027,"text":"Is this disease or treatment different in women?"},{"time":802903,"text":"Now, this is a profound question \nbecause the answer is likely yes,"},{"time":806491,"text":"but your doctor may not know \nthe answer, at least not yet."},{"time":810188,"text":"But if you ask the question, \nyour doctor will very likely"},{"time":814564,"text":"go looking for the answer."},{"time":816846,"text":"And this is so important,"},{"time":819183,"text":"not only for ourselves,"},{"time":821345,"text":"but for all of those whom we love."},{"time":823998,"text":"Whether it be a mother, a daughter, a sister,"},{"time":828482,"text":"a friend or a grandmother."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832179,"text":"It was my grandmother's suffering"},{"time":834322,"text":"that inspired my work"},{"time":836255,"text":"to improve the health of women."},{"time":839240,"text":"That's her legacy."},{"time":841590,"text":"Our legacy can be to improve the health of women"},{"time":846259,"text":"for this generation"},{"time":848398,"text":"and for generations to come."}]},{"cues":[{"time":851420,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":853569,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}